title: eoi
desc: Seaweed-enriched pasta is a type of pasta that includes seaweed or seaweed extracts in its ingredients. This addition enhances the nutritional value of the pasta by providing essential minerals and vitamins, such as iodine and various antioxidants. It may also offer a subtle oceanic flavor and a unique greenish hue, making it not only a healthy choice but also a flavorful one.
